SubjectBuctouche MicMac Band Extension, New Brunswick ** Creation **
PrecisOrder Setting apart 89.62 hectares (221.45 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Buctouche MicMac Band as BUCTOUCHE MICMAC BAND EXTENSION, located in Kent County, Parish of Saint Mary, approximately 9 kilometres from the Village of Saint-Antoine, New Brunswick.
